  "title": "Admin Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>Perform general administrative duties such as filing systems, typing, copying, binding, scanning, office stationery etc.</p><p>Manage day-to-day administrative tasks and office operations.</p><p>Maintain proper filing and systematic organization of office documents. </p><p>To arrange and co-ordinate import/export and transshipment to ensure timely arrivals and handle all related documents. </p><p>Prepare of shipping documents such as Commercial Invoice, Packing list, certificate of origin, and other documents</p><p>Handle procurement support such as purchases requisitions, purchase orders, DO and Invoice tracking.</p><p>Arrange courier of samples and documents</p><p>Check and maintain delivery documents and perform data entry.</p><p>Provide administrative support to management and other departments as needed.</p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>Minimum Diploma holder or GCE O Level with at least 1 years of relevant working experience. </p><p>Proficient in Microsoft Office Suite (Word, Excel, PowerPoint, Teams).</p><p>Strong organizational and time-management skills</p><p>Ability to multitask and work independently in a fast-paced environment.</p><p>Good communication skills and a positive learning attitude.</p>",
